description:
IC1848 - The Soul Of The Milky Way

Equipment
Williamoptics RedCat 51
Celestronuniverse Edge HD 8” w/Hyperstar
Zwoasi 1600mm x2, 224MC, 30mm Guide Scope, ASIAIR, ASIAIR PRO, & EAF
Baaderplanetarium F2 HA, OIII, & SII, Astronomik HA, OIII, & SII Filters
Skywatcherusa EQ6-R Mount

Acquisition
-SII - 432x90” (10.8hrs) HS & 177x180” (8.85hrs) RC 10/28 - 19.65hrs
HA - 388x90” (9.7hrs) HS & 152x180” (7.6hrs) RC 11/4 - 17.3hrs
OIII - 420x90” (10.25hrs) HS & 202x180” (10.1hrs) RC 10/21 - 20.35hrs
-57.30hrs Total Integration Time
-50 Darks, 50 Flats, 250 Bias per session
-Gain 139
-Temp-15c
-Bortle 5

@itz_reg was gracious enough to give me his data to add to my stack:
SII - 9hrs
HA - 8.35hrs
OIII - 8.40hrs
- 25.75 Total integration Time

This stack has a total integration time of 83.05hrs!
